$num - number

$ksp - structural unit code
$ksp_author - Author's structural unit code

$numKsp_sender - serial number within the participant's structural unit (Stage - Sender)

$sc - confidentiality stamps (through commas)
$yyyy - current year
$yy - current year
$date - prints the current date, in the format DDMMYYYY (14092020)
$newnum - each day begins with number 1
